===Etymology===
From {{der|en|grc|πτερόν||wing, feather}} + {{m|grc|ποδός}}, genitive singular of {{m|grc|πούς||foot, leg}}. Equivalent to {{confix|en|ptero|pod}}.

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

